<chapter id="get-started">
    <title>Getting Started</title>
    <abstract>
        <para>
            OTRS::GI is a flexible system to allow web service interconnection with other systems or applications.
            It allow to OTRS act as a provider (server, requested from remote) or requester (client, requesting of remote).
        </para>
        <para>
            This manual shows how to develop your own OTRS::GI plugins in custom modules and how to create
            the web service connections.
            All this including a scheduler, that support asynchronous event handling.
        </para>
    </abstract>

